data.description:
Charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home located in East Marysville. This home features hard surface flooring, fireplace, open concept floor plan, refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave, washer and electric dryer hook ups, leased solar, central heat and air, fenced backyard and two car garage. Located close to Kynoch Elementary/ Kynoch Pre School and a short drive to Marysville High School. Pets negotiable with additional deposit. Renters insurance required. Tenant responsible for PGE, water, sewer, garbage and maintaining landscaping. WE DO NOT ACCEPT ZILLOW APPLICATIONS YOU WILL NEED TO APPLY WITH US. Available now.

QUALIFICATIONS
600 minimum credit score for ALL applicants
Monthly combined income minimum is 2 1/2 times the rent
1 yr employment with provable income
2 yrs provable rental history
NO EVICTIONS
No bankruptcy within the last year. 

Listed by Mallow Real Estate Services DRE 01864149 all information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Individual verification is recommended. All info is subject to change without notice. Equal Opportunity Housing
